node.title: One dead in Northland quad-bike crash
node.description: A person has died in a quad-bike crash at a private property in Panguru in the Hokianga today.
node.content: ["A person has died in a quad-bike crash at a private property in Panguru in the Hokianga today.", "Emergency services were called to the property at 4.20pm, but the person was confirmed deceased at the scene.", "The matter will be referred to the Coroner."]
